DOI: 10.1186/s13690-022-01011-0
PMCID: PMC9758921
PMID: 36527095

Conflict of interest statement: HVO is Editor-in-Chief of Archives of Public 
Health. The authors declare that they have no competing interests.


238. Public Health Nurs. 2023 Mar;40(2):229-242. doi: 10.1111/phn.13158. Epub
