Burden of stroke and its risk factors in Yunnan Province of China, 1990-2017.

Liu L(1), Yang Y(1), Zhao Y(1), Zhang T(1).

Author information:
(1)School of Public Health, Dali University, 22 Wanhua Road, Dali City, Dali Bai 
